data.description: This inviting 4-bed, 3-bath home, designed by a local architect, features original wide plank wood floors, wood ceiling beams, and a free-standing iron stove. The kitchen offers unique charm, featuring granite countertops, a tile backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. The fully finished walkout basement has a family/rec room, exposed brick arched wall and guest or in-law suite with full bathroom as well as laundry room.  The basement has its own separate entrance way providing convenience as well as privacy. The attached garage has a workshop area and an additional room for a studio or office. With ample space, there is endless possibility for hosting guests or simply enjoying the extra room for activities. Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, and bus lines, the home also offers a private wooded backyard with a peaceful stream, perfect for enjoying nature from the deck or gazebo.
